values:
I can safely say, last night was the worst night, of ALL TIME! I had the worst two dreams, in order, of ALL time! Ugh, I got to bed sometime after 1:00AM.&nbsp;I was really happy, because although I was up from 10:30PM-then unable to think of anything except the last two nights, I was still going to get a fair amount of sleep based on how tired I was. You know, that feeling right before you fall asleep? Well, it hit me, and then the worst dream EVER! Or so I thought...

So, apparently I was getting married in my dream, xD, which is strange, I've had dreams where I got married before, but in general, the ceremony never happened in the dream, while in this one, it did. Anyway, I go to the room where my bride should be, I had gone to the bathroom for whatever reason after the ceremony, and, I REALLY wish I hadn't gone and opened the door to THAT room. Ugh, and let me just say, I don't know WHO that dude was... *shudders*

Well, needless to say I woke up, and ugh, it was not fun, I fell back asleep quickly, only to have the SAME DAMN DREAM, BUT WORSE! This time... *shuuuuuuuuuuuuuuudder* my BROTHER was there... and you can bet where he came in... I woke up from that one, and took a bath, for about an hour.&nbsp;
